{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/pages/jupyter-notebook-style","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"ij.Log"}},"markdownRemark":{"html":"<blockquote>\n<p>이 글은 jupyter notebook 의 font, 글자 크기, 간격 등을 수정하는 방법에 관한 글이다</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"1-setting-file\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-setting-file\" aria-label=\"1 setting file permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. Setting file</h1>\n<h2 id=\"command\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#command\" aria-label=\"command permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>command</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">.jupyter</code> 디렉토리가 이미 있다면 아래 명령어 실행은 생략해도 괜찮다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>아래 명령어를 실행하여 jupyter notebook 설정을 위한 파일을 생성할 수 있다.\n파일은 일반적으로 <code class=\"language-text\">C:\\Users\\USERNAME\\</code> 하위에 생성된다. 명령어를 실행했을 때, <code class=\"language-text\">.jupyter</code> 디렉토리가 생성되었는지를 확인하면 된다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\">jupyter notebook --generate-config</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h1 id=\"2-create-css-file\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-create-css-file\" aria-label=\"2 create css file permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. create css file</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>위에서 생성한 디렉토리 아래에 <code class=\"language-text\">/custom/custom.css</code> 파일을 생성하여 jupyter notebook 설정을 할 수 있다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>파일의 전체 경로: <code class=\"language-text\">C:\\Users\\USERNAME\\.jupyter\\custom\\custom.css</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"customizing\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#customizing\" aria-label=\"customizing permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>customizing</h2>\n<h4 id=\"overall-font-style\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#overall-font-style\" aria-label=\"overall font style permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>overall font style</h4>\n<p>전체적인 폰트 스타일은 아래 코드로 지정할 수 있다. jupyter notebook 의 기본 font은 <code class=\"language-text\">Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif</code>인데  아마도 <code class=\"language-text\">Arial</code>을 사용하는 것 같다.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Helvetica</code>를 다운받아볼까..</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>해당 폰트는 markdown 출력 폰트에도 영향을 끼치니 따로 수정하는게 귀찮다면 body 폰트를 한번에 수정하면 된다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-css line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-family</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'AppleSDGothicNeo'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'nanumbarungothic'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> sans-serif<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> </code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"code-style\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#code-style\" aria-label=\"code style permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>code style</h4>\n<p>jupyter notebook의 기본 폰트 스타일은 코딩용 폰트가 아니라 가독성이 떨어진다.</p>\n<p>아래 코드로 code style을 변경할 수 있으며, 개인 취향에 따라 변경하면 된다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-css line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* change cell index: in [n] */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">div.prompt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-family</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'D2Coding'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Consolas<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">calc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>12px + .3vh<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/*change code font*/</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.CodeMirror</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-family</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'D2Coding'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Consolas<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">calc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>12px + .3vh<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">line-height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 140%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"output-text-font-style\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#output-text-font-style\" aria-label=\"output text font style permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>output text font-style</h4>\n<p>출력 글자의 스타일을 지정한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-css line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* output text font style */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">div.output_text pre</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-family</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'D2Coding'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Consolas<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">calc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>12px + .3vh<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">line-height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 140%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"markdown-text-style\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#markdown-text-style\" aria-label=\"markdown text style permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>markdown text style</h4>\n<p>markdown 으로 출력된 글자 스타일을 지정한다. </p>\n<p>코드의 경우 background 색상을 약간 어둡게 하였다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-css line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* code block */</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">div.text_cell_render pre</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1em 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">div.text_cell_render code</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> auto<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> block<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-family</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'D2Coding'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Consolas<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #f3f3f3e8<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<p>추가로 변경하고 싶은 부분이 있을 때마다 추가하면 될 듯 하다</p>","excerpt":"이 글은 jupyter notebook 의 font, 글자 크기, 간격 등을 수정하는 방법에 관한 글이다 1. Setting file command  디렉토리가 이미 있다면 아래 명령어 실행은 생략해도 괜찮다. 아래 명령어를 실행하여 jupyter…","frontmatter":{"date":"2021-01-26","update":"2021-03-02","title":"[devenv] Jupyter notebook 폰트, 스타일 변경","tags":["dev env","python"],"keywords":null},"fields":{"slug":"/pages/jupyter-notebook-style"},"tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/pages/jupyter-notebook-style/#1-setting-file\">1. Setting file</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/pages/jupyter-notebook-style/#command\">command</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/pages/jupyter-notebook-style/#2-create-css-file\">2. create css file</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/pages/jupyter-notebook-style/#customizing\">customizing</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/pages/jupyter-notebook-style"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2827402515","694178885"]}